[SHORT DESC]
Cures sleep.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>The Awakening heals the status of sleep from one Pokemon when used by the trainer. If a Pokemon holds Awakening as an item, it will not activate even if the holder is asleep.</p>

<h2>Location</h2>
<p>All PokeMarts after obtaining one badge, 250 Pokemon Dollars</p>